title: AMRAP MENTALITY: How to Get Optimal Results In Everything You Do ft. Jason Khalipa, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO298
itunes:title: AMRAP MENTALITY: How to Get Optimal Results In Everything You Do ft. Jason Khalipa, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO298
description: How can you develop the kind of mindset that goes all in, all the time? I’m talking about the mentality that can keep the pedal on the gas…to get optimal results…regardless of whether things are going great for you, or you’re slogging your way through tough times. My guest Jason Khalipa is a Crossfit icon & a hugely successful entrepreneur. He’s won competitions at the highest levels, made millions of dollars, & led his family through his little daughter’s brutal encounter with leukemia. Through ups & downs, he knows what it takes to consistently crush it in business & life.
